## Dependencies
- **Python** â€“ Primary language
- **Typer** â€“ CLI framework
- **Pydantic** â€“ Data validation
- **Rich** â€“ Enhanced terminal output
- **google-generativeai & langchain-google-genai** â€“ AI model integration
